DOCUMENTATION
-------------

"Typography and Text Editing in the Text Layout Framework" contains Flex 4.0 projects related to my 360|Flex presentation of the same name.  The slides for the presentation can be found at http://www.slideshare.net/queencodemonkey/typography-text-editing-in-the-text-layout-framework.

The library project QCMTLFLib contains common components used in examples.

There are also example projects demonstrating usage of Adobe's Text Layout Framework including:
	360Flex: all example applications used in my September 22nd presentation.
	Pagination: example of implementing pagination with TLF.